result.name: MOS Burger

reviews.text:
Very affordable burgers. I love their variety, they all have a quintessentially Japanese flair. Interesting pumpkin burger.

They also have different types of sides, you can order a salad to pivot towards the healthier end of the food pyramid.

What you would expect from a MOS burger; clean and tasty. It is a rather smaller branch with a more limited choice of seating, but we did manage to find a seat without much of a wait. Staff are friendly and polite, and food arrives after a short wait. We did sit for a rather extended period and never did staff try to ask us to leave, which I must applaud, especially for Hong Kong.
Nice place to share your happiness here. Quiet and clean table and seat.
Great burgers but small portion and I had to order 2 for dinner!
Good burger... Japanese style
